articles.title: White House officially marks 1 million American deaths from Covid and pushes Congress for more funding - CNN
articles.description: President Joe Biden on Thursday mourned 1 million American deaths from Covid-19, using the occasion to again urge Congress to pass additional funding to control the pandemic.
